<p>In this episode, <a href="http://jjj.me">John James Jacoby</a> and I discuss the recent acquisition of the Google Analytics Dashboard for WordPress plugin, rebuilding the WordPress edit screen, and an in-depth conversation on the concerns expressed surrounding WordPress 4.9.6. We send a shout out to Alex Mills, get an update on John&#8217;s stolen goats, and rant about lawn care power equipment.</p>
